11/12/2021 451 ENDORSED LETTER as to Ghislaine Maxwell addressed to Judge Alison J. Nathan from Matthew Russell Lee, dated 10/29/2021, re: timely opposition to blanket requests to seal portions of motions in limine, trial exhibits, public access. ENDORSEMENT: The Court received the attached letters via email. This District no longer permits public access by telephone for in-court criminal proceedings, including trials. The memorandum can be found here - https:// nysd.uscourts.gov/covid-19-coronavirus. The Courts public access orders for all proceedings in the case can be found here - https://www.nysd.uscourts.gov/usa-vsghislaine-maxwell-20-cr-330-ajn-caseinformation. The Court has implemented a procedure for docketing filings with proposed redactions and is ruling on the proposals as expeditiously as possible. See Dkt. No. 401. SO ORDERED. (Signed by Judge Alison J. Nathan on 11/12/2021) (Inl) (Entered: 11/12/2021)
